## 📊 **Content Management**
### **Service Data Structure**
```typescript
interface Service {
  title: string;
  description: string;
  icon: IconComponent;
  link: string;
  color: string;
  features: string[];
  price?: string;
  category?: string;
}
```
### **Blog Post Structure**
```typescript
interface BlogPost {
  id: number;
  title: string;
  excerpt: string;
  category: string;
  isFeatured: boolean;
  featuredImage: string;
  author: Author;
  publishedDate: string;
  readTime: string;
  slug: string;
  tags: string[];
}
```
